🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to display all even numbers from 1 to 50.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE even_numbers()
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    i INT;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN 1..50 LOOP
        IF i % 2 = 0 THEN
            RAISE NOTICE '%', i;
        END IF;
    END LOOP;
END;
$$;


